freevo (1.5.0-0pre1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release
  * Removed the Vera Truetype fonts from the packages since they are
    available in Debian
  * Reduced the dependencies to allow alternates
  * Add the HTML documentation

 -- Aubin Paul <debian@outlyer.org>  Sun, 21 Mar 2004 10:00:19 -0500

freevo (1.4.1cvs20040109-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New snapshot
  * Replaced `pwd` with $(CURDIR)
  * Fixed postinst
  * Removed spurious warnings from BSD support
  * Remove non-standard mixer, favour ossmixer instead
  * Use dh_install instead of copying by hand.

 -- Aubin Paul <debian@outlyer.org>  Thu,  8 Jan 2004 11:03:45 -0500

